---
title: Sichuan Garlic Plant-Based Mince Tacos with Pickled Onion
description: If you like bold flavours and Asian cuisines, you’ll love food from the Sichuan province in China! We’ve dialled down the chilli but
kept the tasty garlic and umami flavours for an easy-to-eat taco that will appeal to everyone.

